        "content": "<p>I started getting this errors in my kernel module - is it related to rust-analyzer? How can I fix this?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>rust-analyzer:<span class=\"w\"> </span>proc<span class=\"w\"> </span>macro<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>module<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>not<span class=\"w\"> </span>expanded:<span class=\"w\"> </span>Cannot<span class=\"w\"> </span>create<span class=\"w\"> </span>expander<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-for-linux/rust/libmacros.so:<span class=\"w\"> </span>mismatched<span class=\"w\"> </span>ABI<span class=\"w\"> </span>expected:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>rustc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>.80.1<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>3f5fd8dd4<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2024</span>-08-06<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>,<span class=\"w\"> </span>got<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>rustc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>.81.0<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>eeb90cda1<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2024</span>-09-04<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>unresolved-proc-macro<span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>root@asahi-server:~/openvpn-dco#<span class=\"w\"> </span>uname<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a\nLinux<span class=\"w\"> </span>asahi-server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">6</span>.11.0-rc4+<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"c1\">#1 SMP PREEMPT_DYNAMIC Tue Aug 20 22:31:04 +10 2024 aarch64 GNU/Linux</span>\nroot@asahi-server:~/openvpn-dco#<span class=\"w\"> </span>rustc<span class=\"w\"> </span>--version\nrustc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>.81.0<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>eeb90cda1<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2024</span>-09-04<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nroot@asahi-server:~/openvpn-dco#<span class=\"w\"> </span>rustup<span class=\"w\"> </span>--version\nrustup<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>.27.1<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>54dd3d00f<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2024</span>-04-24<span class=\"o\">)</span>\ninfo:<span class=\"w\"> </span>This<span class=\"w\"> </span>is<span class=\"w\"> </span>the<span class=\"w\"> </span>version<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>the<span class=\"w\"> </span>rustup<span class=\"w\"> </span>toolchain<span class=\"w\"> </span>manager,<span class=\"w\"> </span>not<span class=\"w\"> </span>the<span class=\"w\"> </span>rustc<span class=\"w\"> </span>compiler.\ninfo:<span class=\"w\"> </span>The<span class=\"w\"> </span>currently<span class=\"w\"> </span>active<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>rustc<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>version<span class=\"w\"> </span>is<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>rustc<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>.81.0<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>eeb90cda1<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2024</span>-09-04<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>\nroot@asahi-server:~/openvpn-dco#<span class=\"w\"> </span>rust-analyzer<span class=\"w\"> </span>--version\nrust-analyzer<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>.81.0<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>eeb90cda<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2024</span>-09-04<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nroot@asahi-server:~/openvpn-dco#<span class=\"w\"> </span>cat<span class=\"w\"> </span>~/rust-for-linux/.config<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>grep<span class=\"w\"> </span>rust\n<span class=\"nv\">CONFIG_BUILD_SALT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"easy-peasy-rust\"</span>\n<span class=\"nv\">CONFIG_RUSTC_VERSION_TEXT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"rustc 1.81.0 (eeb90cda1 2024-09-04)\"</span>\nroot@asahi-server:~/openvpn-dco#\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/Ghid-8ThUDi2oIi0gXAcAakk/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/Ghid-8ThUDi2oIi0gXAcAakk/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"710x374\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/35136/Ghid-8ThUDi2oIi0gXAcAakk/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
